## Why Event Driven Architecture is Useful

Advantages:

- Systems are independent from each other
- Easy to extend with new components
- Faster reaction to important events
- Better scalability

---

## Summary

This example shows how an **event driven system** can manage emergency situations in a building.  
Different components react to the same event without directly depending on each other, which makes the system more flexible and reliable.
